## Gate A Objectives
<!-- Gate A confirms that the opportunity is well understood, feasibility has been assessed, and there is sufficient justification to proceed to Phase 2 (Inception). -->

Gate A validates:
- The opportunity is clearly defined and aligned to business strategy
- Feasibility has been assessed across technical, commercial, and AI/ML dimensions
- Key stakeholders are identified and engaged
- Risks are understood and initial mitigations planned
- There is a clear decision: PROCEED / HOLD / KILL

